Can we create responsible and ethical GAI through data filtering and AI regulations? {Ethical use of GenAI [F4]}, {Regulations and legal issues related to GenAI [F3]}

What biases could be introduced into GAI by the training data and processes? {GenAI bias mitigation [F4]}

How can we reduce the biases in GAI? How can AI laws and regulations be tailored to account for GAI? {GenAI bias mitigation [F4]}, {Regulations and legal issues related to GenAI [F3]}

Are the current intellectual property rights protection applicable for GAI? {Regulations and legal issues related to GenAI [F3]}

How can we develop a more comprehensive set of metrics for intellectual property rights protection that applies to GAI? {Regulations and legal issues related to GenAI [F3]}, {Definition of GenAI metrics [F5]}

