How can GAI be used appropriately to improve the learning experience and achievement of students? {GenAI adoption and acceptance factors [F2]}

How will the use of GAI impact users’ information search behavior? {Psychological effects of GenAI use on individuals [F1]}

How will the use of GAI impact users’ decision-making process? {Psychological effects of GenAI use on individuals [F1]}

How can individuals find their position and significance when interacting with GAI? {Psychological effects of GenAI use on individuals [F1]}, {Personalization tailored to the individual user [F1]}

How will human-AI relationships evolve as GAI further improves and advances? {Psychological effects of GenAI use on individuals [F1]}

How to build human-machine symbiotic relationships to augment intelligence? {Formation of hybrid human-AI teams [F2]}, {User-GenAI interaction design [F1]}

How should the human(s) and GAI collaborate in a hybrid team? {Formation of hybrid human-AI teams [F2]}

What is the most effective design process for creating GAI that collaborates with humans? {Design principles for GenAI solutions [F5]}

